Description: Product Description: The most splendid way to carry your beautiful belongings. Carry your items in style in this superb slouchy bag, displaying the iconic cream and black stripes, a burgundy panel and beautiful decorative stitching; also featuring a handy buttoned patch pocket and an adjustable brown leather-style strap. This bag delightfully displays the alluring Lost For Words in mysterious shades of blues and gorgeous greys. Pull open the buckle style, press stud fastening and open the jet black zip by the golden heart shaped pull to find a large lined compartment, for your purse, books and other bits and bobs. You will also find a zipped pocket, two smaller pockets and an elasticated lobster clasp for your keys ...to help keep your bag organised. Cleaning Instructions: Wipe clean with a damp cloth. Approx. Bag Size: 415mm wide x 405mm high x 80mm deep at base. Single Adjustable Strap Size: 4cm wide x 65cm long. Note: These Bags should be kept away from fire. Each Gorjuss bag is hand-finished and as a result colour and detail will vary from piece to piece. Please be aware of colour transfer if rubbed against a lighter coloured fabric.
